{"tid":452302,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(多圖多字多資料)8日7夜四國去完又想再去之旅","createTime":"2017-10-30T05:17:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T09:03:03.000Z","uid":115811,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"576f98ca0a6ef6d07269bc29da5dd930805f5cfc","tid":452302,"uid":115811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T05:17:28.000Z","msg":"小編會將去四國既行程，圖文並茂咁介紹比大家。<br />\n<br />\n四國位於中國地區的南邊，中間夾著瀨戶內海，由德島縣、香川縣、愛媛縣、高知縣共4個縣構成。 如果去得太多大城市，想去比較少遊客，又寧靜既地方，咁就一定要去一次四國啦。 <br />\n<br />\n希望依個行程作為大家出發前既一個參考，如果計劃去四國既朋友，就唔好錯過啦。<br />\n<br />\n有人想睇就會慢慢出post!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n介紹番個行程先:<br />\nDay 1:<br />\n大阪 &gt; 德島 ＞阿波おどり会館<br />\nDay 2:<br />\n德島 &gt; 風呂ノ谷&rdquo;小便岩 &gt; かずら橋 &gt; 高知<br />\nDay 3:<br />\n高知 &gt; 四万十川 &gt; 松山<br />\nDay 4: <br />\n松山 &gt; サンライズ糸山 &gt; タオル美術館ＩＣＨＩＨＩＲＯ &gt; 道後商店街<br />\nDay 5: <br />\n松山 &gt; 下灘 &gt; 三越松山店 &gt; 高松<br />\nDay 6:<br />\n高松 &gt; 直島<br />\nDay 7:<br />\n高松 &gt; 小豆島<br />\nDay 8:<br />\n高松 &gt; 大阪 &gt; 香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/131723_152d6c0b769f61d9713f0db67496599b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F131723_152d6c0b769f61d9713f0db67496599b.jpg&h=8b31b4d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2f74ca56e1d5bbcaf151860eb55c2afa0f82d94","tid":452302,"uid":19310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T05:23:02.000Z","msg":"留名先, 我四國差德島未去, 去埋就去晒d大路景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1e41ce52327593f304b7bf508b5fdaf6abe8255","tid":452302,"uid":115811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T05:43:38.000Z","msg":"放多幾張相毒下大家先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/134314_dfacea0ed14a3da69456c803678c3565.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F134314_dfacea0ed14a3da69456c803678c3565.jpg&h=e6ce42e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/134319_dc91d3c4247c17a91254ad4f0daf044d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F134319_dc91d3c4247c17a91254ad4f0daf044d.jpg&h=f7f61ab3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/134322_a2a630ff0c08e2b56514edf520e746d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F134322_a2a630ff0c08e2b56514edf520e746d5.jpg&h=48759ab4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a3a76fada57e7ccc67e566013cd457b177ad3ee","tid":452302,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T05:52:14.000Z","msg":"車費？"},{"pid":"ae9ac62b958241126579a9a3fc0a8eff3a20c5fc","tid":452302,"uid":115811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:33:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>車費？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n主要買左張四國pass，一pass旁身，四國通行。所以有上面既行程"},{"pid":"8ff214f993128518b86788fa73e28ca49748556e","tid":452302,"uid":27323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:37:14.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"21a307d1695a0e62c3cd6faa435ae3fa2428b4e0","tid":452302,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:49:43.000Z","msg":"海景最愛"},{"pid":"4d8d66117c239aff63f3f4d395d65b99929a6965","tid":452302,"uid":27665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:51:12.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"5d78da446a510333ae2c10b6062fae86b4f8103b","tid":452302,"uid":115811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T07:13:47.000Z","msg":"小弟文筆未必好，行程亦未必係最好，請多多指教。不過有咩四國行程問題，幫到都一定幫手。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去之前已經預備晒所有野，上網做足功課。所以今次去四國，基本上唔難搵路，當然我去既景點大部分比較係熱門。<br />\n<br />\nDay 1:<br />\n大阪 &gt; 德島 ＞阿波おどり会館<br />\n<br />\n小弟坐CX07:55 am由香港到大阪，到達大阪差唔多12:30pm，之後第一時間\t從國際線南到達口向左前進, 1/F在JAL ABC到達宅配櫃台辦理貨物託運去地下寄行李，因為我無理由拎個行李行四萬十川呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/144611_9b2cbb636f7366d5152dff39f555040c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F144611_9b2cbb636f7366d5152dff39f555040c.jpg&h=5dd71a5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/144612_aac6551882bf1f0ccd44f51176307589.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F144612_aac6551882bf1f0ccd44f51176307589.jpg&h=0a6d0b86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要寫既大約係:<br />\n荷物 luggage:<br />\n愛媛県松山市XXXXXXXXX<br />\ntel: XXXXXXXXX<br />\nArrival Date: xx/xx<br />\nWe arrive on xx/xx<br />\nxxxxxxx@xxx.com<br />\n<br />\n其實係機場寄野唔難又平，我一個行李大約HK$100就搞掂。我個行李就寄去松山酒店。當然你要放定多兩條under係背囊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/145043_32ff9df9e810190a8338604fdb93b321.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F145043_32ff9df9e810190a8338604fdb93b321.jpg&h=9e38b9fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後就搭巴士由大阪機場去德島，最好睇個巴士時間表做人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/145319_3be6ddbe725cee93b0ebb9772bf117e6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F145319_3be6ddbe725cee93b0ebb9772bf117e6.png&h=2429668f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔係有排等，真係要等既，食左個午餐先出發<br />\n<br />\n最後我搭既時間如下:<br />\n關西機場 14:20/16:10 徳島車站17:05/18:55<br />\n第一航廈  地下2號巴士站(往淡路・鳴門・德島)  售票處(車站隔離)  德島車站(總站落)<br />\n3700円, 90mins<br />\n<br />\n由於去鳴門唔夠時間，加上有朋友去完，坐個架船出海會嘔，所以放棄左。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/145831_59c1170b4ee4b0a126fad06d33b22b0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F145831_59c1170b4ee4b0a126fad06d33b22b0b.jpg&h=ef4a4e68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/145844_b91b2cb1dac7e87620d285662335bdbf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F145844_b91b2cb1dac7e87620d285662335bdbf.jpg&h=cc5d63d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nダイワロイネットホテル徳島駅前<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/150653_79607ed14447588844acaeade222fe1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F150653_79607ed14447588844acaeade222fe1e.jpg&h=f69b1d26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/150700_3699ef382fae01bef3aa203808251458.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F150700_3699ef382fae01bef3aa203808251458.jpg&h=fc463a39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢地開業只有幾年，所以好多野都好新。感覺良好<br />\n<br />\n其實個總站好近德島車站，所以我訂酒店都訂係車站隔離，因為依幾日都要早起身出發。<br />\n<br />\n落左車就去換四國pass，買左張pass，基本上坐指定席都唔洗補錢，唔怪得年年都蝕錢啦。除左有次坐green car之外。<br />\n<br />\n買四國pass資料<br />\n<a href=\"http://shikoku-railwaytrip.com/tw/railpass.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fshikoku-railwaytrip.com%2Ftw%2Frailpass.html&d=AGvHFC3Ye9q1nZzXwKH0%2F0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=d17b20ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://shikoku-railwaytrip.com/tw/railpass.html</a><br />\n<br />\n之後去左酒店check in後，第一時間行去阿波おどり会館<br />\n買飛先，地址如下:<br />\n徳島市新町橋2丁目20番地 2/F<br />\n大人800円 毎日20:00～20:50<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/151012_69d526f309f4539e11aca8f4471e17bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F151012_69d526f309f4539e11aca8f4471e17bc.jpg&h=b39ab606&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/151021_ccce771ed97a789ec821e921e387291a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F151021_ccce771ed97a789ec821e921e387291a.jpg&h=03b1777c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/151022_dec591f7f6f5c13377a87f4a485b9d51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F151022_dec591f7f6f5c13377a87f4a485b9d51.jpg&h=a81db8a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/151023_00f7bfcad17abddc29938a474ad6e645.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F151023_00f7bfcad17abddc29938a474ad6e645.jpg&h=fc9101e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買完飛就去東大填肚，佢既湯雖然比較濃，但佢係我係四國裡面，覺得最好食個餐麵店。<br />\nラーメン東大　大道本店 <br />\n阿波おどり会館 步行8mins / 返JR德島站步行 16mins<br />\n地址:<br />\n徳島県徳島市大道1-36<br />\n營業時間:<br />\n11:00~4:00 (年中無休)<br />\nTabelog介紹:<br />\n<a href=\"http://tabelog.com/tokushima/A3601/A360101/36000013\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftabelog.com%2Ftokushima%2FA3601%2FA360101%2F36000013&d=AGvHFC3Ye9q1nZzXwKH0%2F0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=59b7f3d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tabelog.com/tokushima/A3601/A360101/36000013</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/151133_7e2e51c65dc04b2107228a201e957940.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F151133_7e2e51c65dc04b2107228a201e957940.jpg&h=98a5fa00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/151135_d1d51be9acf2ccbe0c8cd41928d2058b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F151135_d1d51be9acf2ccbe0c8cd41928d2058b.jpg&h=27e0462e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/151137_0f2878b0a484924d38f6dc06f3ac621f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F151137_0f2878b0a484924d38f6dc06f3ac621f.jpg&h=f794b8bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食完東大，就行番去睇阿波舞。其實行番去會場好近。見仲有時間，係會場影下相，買紀念品，之後入場睇阿波舞。<br />\n<br />\n雖然唔明佢地講咩，但見到觀眾可以出去同佢地跳埋一份，又有人係裡面寫生，男女老少一齊輕鬆一下。這種旅遊睇驗，每次旅程都應該只少有一次。<br />\n<br />\n介紹住咁多，希望大家多多支持，唔好爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d330310bef986d712bef79bc9485b4a6f4e1b9","tid":452302,"uid":145219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T08:44:34.000Z","msg":"請問樓主你呢個everydayjapan係咪一個blog/page，有無其他遊記可以睇?"},{"pid":"263618af7a9c92d7b69cbbbb57070ed7d9c7ab77","tid":452302,"uid":115811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T09:03:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請問樓主你呢個everydayjapan係咪一個blog/page，有無其他遊記可以睇?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你可以去facebook search &quot;everydayjapan&quot; or 日日遊，其實我寫左唔少地方，想幫下唔太熟路既巴絲，專業線我就未到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇完覺得有用就係裡面支持下啦, 謝謝"}]}